✅ What this shows:
•	MBT orbital law matches Kepler’s predictions across the board (even comets and Sedna).
•	MBT gravity law matches Newton/GR predictions without needing mass or G.
•	The two frameworks give the same outcomes, but MBT explains them via motion + geometry instead of mass + force.
 

